posts.post_content:
FS:  N321 S.F. Hess & Co. Joseph Noonan.

Very rare California league of Joseph Noonan.  You dont see these often and this card shows moderate corner wear, but has a very clean back.
As you may be able to see on the scan, the card has some minor creases, but no paper loos and has very nice eye appeal.  
A very nice example of this super rare 19th century baseball card.
